summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 2712, for the improvement of West 65th Street, form 15th Avenue Northwest, to 28th Avenue Northwest; and certain parts of certain other streets and avenues all in the City of Seattle, by grading and resurfacing, constructing wooden curbs and gutters, concrete sidewalks thereon, and providing for the necessary surface drainage,, under Ordinance No. 31931 and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
